## Roadmap  
- [ ] Expand caregiver dashboard  
- [ ] Add memory prompts & journaling feature  
- [ ] Optional music-based memory jogs (AI-curated playlists)  
- [ ] HIPAA-compliant hosting option  

## Why It Matters  
Memory Lane started as a personal tool for family caregiving and has grown into a vision for **accessible AI-driven independence**. It’s not just about reminders — it’s about supporting autonomy, connection, and quality of life.  

